				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$m_{R}$$\end{document}. Furthermore, when the coexistence criterion does not coincide with the bifurcation conditions, the pest density \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
