				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$m_P$$\end{document}). Figure 7 (left side) presents the graph of this function, highlighting the darker regions where the cascading effect is most pronounced. On the right side of Fig. 7, the darker regions correspond to combinations of \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
